# xomda.js — Cline / Roo Code Instructions

> **📚 For comprehensive project context**, see `.cursor/rules/KNOWLEDGE_BASE.md` — the unified knowledge base for all AI agents.

xomda.js is a **Model-Driven Architecture (MDA)** platform: a full-stack TypeScript monorepo where users design data models visually and generate code from Handlebars templates.

